SOKO23.title: Dr. Eingali, Master of Evil
SOKO23.description: U7, member of Japan Branch of Unicorn, is the one who controls the gigantic GIANT ROBO with the wrist-watch controller microphone. One day, he receives from his father a parcel as a birthday gift. It is a kit for constructing a man-size robot.

HOLM01.title: A Scandal in Bohemia
HOLM01.path: ../Sherlock Holmes/Sherlock Holmes - 01 A Scandal in Bohemia.m4v
HOLM01.description: Sherlock Holmes finds himself evenly matched when he is employed by the King of Bohemia to retrieve an indiscreet photograph from the American actress and singer, Irene Adler.

LISP30.title: Blast Off Into Space
LISP30.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 30 - Blast Off In Space.m4v
LISP30.description: A space miner is blasting the planet apart and the Robinsons have to leave even though Smith wants to stay and become rich.

LITB111.title: The Spot Removers
LITB111.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 111 The Spot Removers.m4v
LITB111.description: Wally is sure that carefully hanging his jacket in his closet will keep it clean for an upcoming dance, forgetting that he shares the closet with a younger brother whose middle name is trouble!

SPRA46.title: Motorcycle Apaches
SPRA46.description: A astronomical base in the Southwest is being terrorized by a band of apaches on motorcycles, and calls Speed for help.

LITB112.title: Beaver the Model
LITB112.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 112 Beaver the Model.m4v
LITB112.description: The Beaver disobeys Ward by returning an application sent to him by a modeling agency and finds himself in trouble when the agency demands a fee.

CSMS13.title: Who Speaks for Earth?
CSMS13.description: Carl Sagan considers the significance of science and discuss the importance of human survival in the nuclear age.

LISP28.title: A Change of Space
LISP28.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 28 - A Change Of Space.m4v
LISP28.description: A strange interdimensional ship turns Will into a genius and Dr. Smith into an old man.

T39S1935.title: The 39 Steps
T39S1935.description: A Canadian civilian in London becomes caught up in preventing an organisation of spies called "The 39 Steps" from stealing British military secrets. Alfred Hitchcock directs.

LITB113.title: Wally, the Businessman
LITB113.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 113 Wally, the Businessman.m4v
LITB113.description: When Ward gives Wally permission to get a job, Wally discovers that there is more to making money than just selling ice cream bars and that allies come from unlikely places.

LITB114.title: Beaver and Ivanhoe
LITB114.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 114 Beaver and Ivanhoe.m4v
LITB114.description: When Beaver's teacher Miss Landers assigns the class a book to read Ward suggests Ivanhoe, one of his favorite boyhood books. Impressed by the tale of knighthood, Beaver forms his own knight club and sets out to defend his neighborhood.

SPRA45.title: The Great Car Wrestling Match
SPRA45.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 45 The Great Car Wrestling Match.mp4
SPRA45.description: Speed discovers that a former racing driver Gadge Zoomer has taken to car wrestling (demolition derbies) to support his family, and attempts to get him to leave this destructive sport.

LISP31.title: Wild Adventure
LISP31.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 31 - Wild Adventure.m4v
LISP31.description: Smith finds the course back to earth, but a space female lures Smith out of the ship. Saving him would again leave the crew of the Jupiter 2 lost in space.

LITB115.title: Wally's Play
LITB115.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 115 Wally's Play.m4v
LITB115.description: Wally considers it an honor to be inducted into a popular school club but has second thoughts when he finds out what his part will be in the club's annual play.

LISP29.title: Follow the Leader
LISP29.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 29 - Follow The Leader.m4v
LISP29.description: An evil spirit possesses John Robinson and plans to fly the Jupiter 2 back to his home world, even at the expense of Will's life.
